                  "name": "dp",
                  "fill": "$textSecondary",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "Pax Fluxia is the result of my passion for \"visible strategy\"—the belief that you should be able to see the flow of war at a glance. Every ship is an individual dot. Every flow is a visible river of force.\n\nInspired by classics like Galcon and TradeWars 2002, this game is built for the modern browser, combining deep, cerebral tactics with immediate playability.",
